# Supabase Online

- Supabase SDK imports belong only in infrastructure.
- Use the public `anon` key in the frontend; never expose or reference `service_role` in app code.
- Online mode must authenticate with anonymous auth before remote writes.
- All migrations must be idempotent: use `create table if not exists`, `create index if not exists`, and guarded policy creation.
- Enable RLS on every public online table.
- Host-owned tables must enforce ownership through `games.host_user_id = auth.uid()`.
- Edge Functions are out of scope for the MVP; prefer RLS and versioned SQL/RPC only when atomicity is required.
